*Muči* ga strah od glasnih zvukova. (He is tormented by the fear of loud noises.)

*Mučila* ga je činjenica da je izgubio svoju ljubav. (The fact that he had lost his love was tormenting him.)

*Mučenje* se nastavlja i dan danas. (The torment continues to this day.)

*Mučio* je sebe svojim ponašanjem. (He was tormenting himself with his behavior.)

*Muče* ga razmišljanja o svim njegovim greškama. (He is tormented by thoughts of all his mistakes.)